股票動態

股票市場是買賣雙方交易公司股票的地方，也是個人和公司投資的最受歡迎的方式之一。現在估計世界股票市場規模達到數兆。紐約證券交易所位於紐約市，是世界上最大的股票市場。 紐約證券交易所約有2,800家上市公司。在這個問題上，我們將看看其中五家公司的每月股價：IB、通用電氣（GE）、寶潔、可口CocaCola和波音。此問題中使用的數據來自Infochimps。

使用read.csv()下載並讀取以下文件：

  • data/IBMStock.csv
  • data/GEStock.csv
  • data/ProcterGambleStock.csv
  • data/CocaColaStock.csv
  • data/BoeingStock.csv

分別存入資料框IBM、GE、ProcterGamble、CocaCola和Boeing， 每個資料框都有兩個變量，描述如下：

  • Date：日期
  • StockPrice：給定月份公司的平均股價

在這個案例，我們將看看這些公司的股票動態如何隨著時間的推移而發生變化。


#載入資料
IBM= read.csv("data/IBMStock.csv")
GE= read.csv("data/GEStock.csv")
ProcterGamble=read.csv("data/ProcterGambleStock.csv")
CocaCola=read.csv("data/CocaColaStock.csv")
Boeing=read.csv("data/BoeingStock.csv")

Section-1 Summary Statistics

§ 1.1 Our five datasets all have the same number of observations. How many observations are there in each data set?

#每個資料集皆有480筆資料
nrow(IBM)
[1] 480

§ 1.2 What is the earliest year in our datasets?

#先把各資料集的date字串改成日期
IBM$Date=as.Date(IBM$Date, "%m/%d/%y")
GE$Date=as.Date(GE$Date, "%m/%d/%y")
ProcterGamble$Date=as.Date(ProcterGamble$Date, "%m/%d/%y")
CocaCola$Date=as.Date(CocaCola$Date, "%m/%d/%y")
Boeing$Date=as.Date(Boeing$Date, "%m/%d/%y")

#找出最早的年
min(IBM$Date) %>% format("%Y")
[1] "1970"

§ 1.3 What is the latest year in our datasets?

#找出最晚的年
max(IBM$Date) %>% format("%Y")
[1] "2009"

§ 1.4 What is the mean stock price of IBM over this time period?

#找出平均值
mean(IBM$StockPrice)
[1] 144.4

§ 1.5 What is the minimum stock price of General Electric (GE) over this time period?

#找出最小值
min(GE$StockPrice)
[1] 9.294

§ 1.6 What is the maximum stock price of Coca-Cola over this time period?

#找出最大值
max(CocaCola$StockPrice)
[1] 146.6

§ 1.7 What is the median stock price of Boeing over this time period?

#找出中位數
median(Boeing$StockPrice)
[1] 44.88

§ 1.8 What is the standard deviation of the stock price of Procter & Gamble over this time period?

#找出標準差
sd(ProcterGamble$StockPrice)
[1] 18.19

Section-2 Visualizing Stock Dynamics

§ 2.1 Around what year did Coca-Cola has its highest stock price in this time period? Around what year did Coca-Cola has its lowest stock price in this time period?

#找出可口CocaCola最高股價
which.max(CocaCola$StockPrice) 
[1] 37
#找出第37筆可口CocaCola日期中的年份
CocaCola$Date[37]%>% format("%Y") 
[1] "1973"
#結合在一起
CocaCola$Date[which.max(CocaCola$StockPrice)]%>% format("%Y")
[1] "1973"
CocaCola$Date[which.min(CocaCola$StockPrice)]%>% format("%Y")
[1] "1980"

§ 2.2 In March of 2000, the technology bubble burst, and a stock market crash occurred. According to this plot, which company’s stock dropped more?

Ans:ProcterGamble公司股價在2000年3月跌幅最大

#畫出點狀圖，將點改為線，把cocacola設為紅線
plot(CocaCola$Date,CocaCola$StockPrice,type="l",col="red",lwd=3,xlab="Date",ylab="StockPrice")
#加上ProcterGamble公司的線，顏色為藍色
lines(ProcterGamble$Date,ProcterGamble$StockPrice,col="blue",lwd=3)
#畫出題目2000-03的時間點，lwd為線條粗細，lty為線條分段
abline(v=as.Date("2000-03-01"),lwd=3,lty=2,col="green")

§ 2.3 (a) Around 1983, the stock for one of these companies (Coca-Cola or Procter and Gamble) was going up, while the other was going down. Which one was going up?

Ans:CocaCola的公司股價在1983的時候上升

#同上
plot(CocaCola$Date,CocaCola$StockPrice,type="l", col="red",lwd=3,xlab="Date",ylab="StockPrice")
lines(ProcterGamble$Date,ProcterGamble$StockPrice,type="l",col="blue",lwd=3)

#畫出題目1983的時間點
abline(v=as.Date("1983-01-01"),lwd=3,lty=2,col="green")

Section-4 Monthly Trends

§ 4.1 For IBM, compare the monthly averages to the overall average stock price. In which months has IBM historically had a higher stock price (on average)? Select all that apply.

Ans:1.2.3.4.5月平均股價高於總平均股價

#比較每個月的平均股價與總平均股價
tapply(IBM$StockPrice,format(IBM$Date,"%m"),mean) - mean(IBM$StockPrice)>0
   01    02    03    04    05    06    07    08    09    10    11    12 
 TRUE  TRUE  TRUE  TRUE  TRUE FALSE FALSE FALSE FALSE FALSE FALSE FALSE

§ 4.2 General Electric and Coca-Cola both have their highest average stock price in the same month. Which month is this?

Ans:4月

#列出每個月平均股價，並找出最大值
